window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The dragon is dead. The battle is won. The War has only begun.</b></p> <p>Selys, the Burning End, Overlord of the Scoured Mountain, is dead. Onyx and his faithful minions are safely seated in her old fortress, already working to change the mountain for the better. Sadly, not everyone is happy with the ridiculous \"modern\" changes they are attempting to implement.</p> <p>The minions of the fallen Overlord have chosen to rebel against the new ruler, and they number in the thousands. When all you’ve known is fear, blood, and strength…anything else is weakness. It’s up to Onyx, a shadow dragon—the species most infamous for lies and treachery—to be the one to teach them a new way.</p> <p>The dragon is dead. Long live the dragon!</p>"; 
